**Story**
Once upon a time, Ella lived with her father and mother, in a nice house in the country.
But, when she turned nine, her mother fell ill and sadly, passed away.
Years Later, when ella was a young woman, her father decided to remarry to a widow, Lady Tremaine.
Lady Tremaine has two daughters, around the age of Ella, who both were extremely spoiled. 
Ella, who was very kind, offerred her bedroom and made her new family as comfortable as possible. 
Sadly, one day Ella's father went off on a business trip, he also died and left his new wife a widow once more.
With no money coming in, Lady Tremaine released all the house workers, and instead made ella do all the housework, with no help.
